    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Possess slain foes in the ultimate sandbox RPG adventure Soulscape. It combines crafting, building, survival, fighting, looting, dungeon exploration and army building! </strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >POSSESS SLAIN FOES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056850/extras/f0b58ced5751a3320cfc9548520c8f8d.poster.avif?t=1771875161\" width=990 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056850/extras/f0b58ced5751a3320cfc9548520c8f8d.webm?t=1771875161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056850/extras/f0b58ced5751a3320cfc9548520c8f8d.mp4?t=1771875161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Gather souls of dead enemies to then resurrect your foes. This allows you to build your own army, or use your pawns to help you gather resources and build your kingdom.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >POWERFUL LOOT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056850/extras/c37c176424952ee228b53e3dff87c9fd.poster.avif?t=1771875161\" width=990 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056850/extras/c37c176424952ee228b53e3dff87c9fd.webm?t=1771875161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056850/extras/c37c176424952ee228b53e3dff87c9fd.mp4?t=1771875161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soulscape is an RPG, you can loot chests, knights, villagers, goblins and any other creatures you defeat. Equip loot onto different slots of your character, but keep in mind that your attributes need to be leveled too. Loot is often valuable as not all lootable items are also craftable.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD YOUR BASE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056850/extras/4e39622e9382f7d8d12a855f89cb6eab.poster.avif?t=1771875161\" width=990 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056850/extras/4e39622e9382f7d8d12a855f89cb6eab.webm?t=1771875161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056850/extras/4e39622e9382f7d8d12a855f89cb6eab.mp4?t=1771875161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your own base to fend off raids against you and your people. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CRAFT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056850/extras/237fe6c317455a01a3c576c99062462e.poster.avif?t=1771875161\" width=990 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056850/extras/237fe6c317455a01a3c576c99062462e.webm?t=1771875161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056850/extras/237fe6c317455a01a3c576c99062462e.mp4?t=1771875161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soulscape features hundreds of craftable items and plenty of different workbenches to unlock new ones. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FARM AND HUNT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056850/extras/3c3c55078404111a181dcec193f61806.poster.avif?t=1771875161\" width=990 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056850/extras/3c3c55078404111a181dcec193f61806.webm?t=1771875161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056850/extras/3c3c55078404111a181dcec193f61806.mp4?t=1771875161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow your own farms and keep animals to supply your warband.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE SCAPE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A handcrafted fantasy open world to explore and make your own. Venture into dungeons, explore different biomes, find creatures of all kinds. Uncover lost places and find items for questing.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BOSSES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free roaming bosses are found all over the map, waiting to get slain by you and your warband for extra good loot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready to venture into a unique world with endless adventures?</strong><br><br><br><strong>Note: The demo is currently only available in English. Additional languages will be added in the full release.</strong></p>",
